title.rendered: ZKTECO inBio 160 CASE B IP-BASED DOOR ACCESS CONTROL PANEL

content.rendered:
inBio 160 is a One Door Two-Way Biometric

Features

  • User – 30,000
  • Event Buffer – 100,000 transactions
  • Communication – TCP/IP
  • Number of doors controlled – 1 door
  • Number of readers Supported – 4(2 RS-485 Reader, 2 26-bit wiegand reader)
  • Types of readers supported – 26-bit Wiegand and RS485 FR Series Reader
  • Number of Inputs – 3(Exit Button and Door Status, 1 AUX)
  • Number of Outputs – 2 (1-Form C Relay for Lock and One Form C Relay for Aux Output)
